# Astro patterns

- Prefer static generation; use `client:*` only when the UI needs client-side JS.
- Pass data with `Astro.props`; use `getStaticPaths()` for dynamic routes under `src/pages/`.
- Load structured content with `getCollection` and schemas in [`src/content.config.ts`](mdc:src/content.config.ts).
- Blog/TIL post routes and slug helpers live in [`src/lib/content/postRoutes.ts`](mdc:src/lib/content/postRoutes.ts).
- For `src/` layout and where to add files, follow [`02-source-organization.mdc`](mdc:.cursor/rules/02-source-organization.mdc) and root [`AGENTS.md`](mdc:AGENTS.md).
